@using Common.Static
@model Common.ViewModels.Lica.LicaRegisterComposite
@addTagHelper *, Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.TagHelpers


    <table class="table table-bordered table-lica-register col-md-12" id="lica-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 60px;  text-align:center;">ЕГН</th>
                <th style="width: 200px; text-align:center;">Имена</th>
                <th style="width: 60px;  text-align:center;">СИК</th>
                <th style="width: 100px; text-align:center;">Длъжност</th>
                <th style="width: 100px; text-align:center;">Партия</th>
                <th style="width: 100px; text-align:center;">Решение</th>
                <th style="width: 30px;  text-align:center;"></th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>

            @foreach (var lice in Model.AllLica)
            {
                <tr>
                    <td style="height:49px;">@lice.EGN</td>
                    <td>@lice.Names</td>
                    <td>@lice.Sik</td>
                    <td>@lice.Dlujnost</td>
                    <td>@lice.Partia</td>
                    <td>@lice.Reshenie</td>
                    <td>
                        <button onclick="SetPaymentCorrection(this, '@lice.Id')" 
                                class="btn btn-outline-secondary lica-btn-with-icon-table lica-right-input-icon-table-btn" 
                                type="button">
                            <img src="~/img/lica-images/Edit-128.png" 
                                class="lica-right-input-icon-table lica-right-input-icon-table-edit" />
                        </button>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            }

            @if (Model.AllLica.Count < 10)
            {
                @for (var i = 0; i < 10 - Model.AllLica.Count; i++)
                {
                    <tr>
                        <td style="height:49px;"></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                        <td></td>
                    </tr>
                }
            }

        </tbody>
    </table>

<nav aria-label="Page navigation example" 
     class="col-lg-10 col-md-12 ml-auto mr-auto pagination-col mt-2">

    <form asp-area="Obrabotki" 
          asp-controller="Home" 
          asp-action="GetLicaByPage" 
          id="pagination-form">

        <input asp-for="CurrentPage" type="hidden" id="pagination-current-page" />
        <input asp-for="EgnFilter" type="hidden" id="egn-filter-hidden" />

        <ul class="pagination">
            @if (Model.MaxPages > PaginationInfo.NumberOfPages && Model.CurrentPage != 1)
            {
                <li class="page-item">
                    <button class="page-link" onclick="UpdatePagination(this,1,'@Model.EgnFilter')" aria-label="Previous" type="button">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                </li>
            }
            else if (Model.MaxPages > 0)
            {
                <li class="page-item disabled">
                    <button class="page-link" aria-label="Previous" type="button">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                </li>
            }
            @{
                if (Model.MaxPages <= PaginationInfo.NumberOfPages)
                {
                    for (var i = 1; i <= Model.MaxPages; i++)
                    {
                        if (i == Model.CurrentPage)
                        {
                            <li class="page-item active">
                                <button class="page-link" type="button">
                                    @i
                                </button>
                            </li>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <li class="page-item">
                                <button class="page-link" 
                                        onclick="UpdatePagination(this,@i,'@Model.EgnFilter')" 
                                        type="button">
                                    @i
                                </button>
                            </li>
                        }
                    }
                }
                else
                {
                    var startingValue = 1;
                    var endingValue = 3;
                    if (Model.CurrentPage == Model.MaxPages)
                    {
                        startingValue = Model.MaxPages - (PaginationInfo.NumberOfPages) + 1;
                        endingValue = Model.MaxPages;
                    }
                    else if (Model.CurrentPage > 1)
                    {
                        startingValue = Model.CurrentPage - 1;
                        endingValue = Model.CurrentPage + 1;
                    }

                    for (var i = startingValue; i <= endingValue; i++)
                    {
                        if (i == Model.CurrentPage)
                        {
                            <li class="page-item active">
                                <button class="page-link" type="button">
                                    @i
                                </button>
                            </li>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <li class="page-item">
                                <button class="page-link" 
                                        onclick="UpdatePagination(this,@i,'@Model.EgnFilter')" 
                                        type="button">
                                    @i
                                </button>
                            </li>
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.MaxPages > PaginationInfo.NumberOfPages && Model.CurrentPage != Model.MaxPages)
            {
                <li class="page-item">
                    <button class="page-link" onclick="UpdatePagination(this,@Model.MaxPages, '@Model.EgnFilter')" aria-label="Previous" type="button">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </li>
            }
            else if (Model.MaxPages > 0)
            {
                <li class="page-item disabled">
                    <button class="page-link" aria-label="Next" type="button">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </li>
            }

        </ul>
    </form>
</nav>